.SH NAME
HTMLTextAreaElement.value \- HTMLTextAreaElement: value property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]value\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]HTMLTextAreaElement\f[R] interface represents the value of the
\f[CR]<textarea>\f[R] element as a string, which is an empty string if
the widget contains no content.
It returns or sets the raw value contained in the control.
.SH VALUE
A string containing the contents of the \f[CR]<textarea>\f[R] element.
